#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# other
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NoGrabServer
RestartPreviousState
DecorateTransients
showiconmanager
##RandomPlacement

SqueezeTitle
BorderWidth 2
MenuBorderWidth 4
ButtonIndent 2
IconRegion "1300x100-95-1" SOUTH EAST 75 25
ForceIcons
RandomPlacement

